2116
02:15:31,248 --> 02:15:33,834
Am I going to see them?
Am I going to talk to them?

2117
02:15:35,085 --> 02:15:37,296
Don't I have some kind of contact with them?

2118
02:15:38,172 --> 02:15:39,214
