2128
02:16:11,914 --> 02:16:16,001
So, you do whatever, but... that's it.

2129
02:16:17,544 --> 02:16:20,005
- You need Henry, not me, right?
- That's right.

2130
02:16:20,422 --> 02:16:22,883
Frankly, I don't care whether you go or not.

2131
02:16:23,217 --> 02:16:26,595
