2188
02:19:28,235 --> 02:19:32,406
<i>There's no action.
I have to wait around like everyone</i> else.

2189
02:19:32,781 --> 02:19:34,575
<i>Can't even get decent food.</i>

2190
02:19:35,325 --> 02:19:38,453
<i>After I got here I ordered spaghetti
